{"word":"H5081 - נָדִיב - nâdîyb - naw-deeb' - Free","slug":"H5081","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נָדִיב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nâdîyb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>naw-deeb'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Free"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05D3;&#x05D9;&#x05D1; - na&#x0302;d&#x0131;&#x0302;yb</b> - <i>naw-deeb'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5068\">H5068</a>; properly <i>voluntary</i>, that is, generous; hence, <i>magnanimous</i>; as noun, a <i>grandee</i> (sometimes a <i>tyrant</i>): - free, liberal (things), noble, prince, willing ([hearted])."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5068\">H5068</a>, <a href=\"#/H5070\">H5070</a>, <a href=\"#/H5071\">H5071</a>, <a href=\"#/H5072\">H5072</a>, <a href=\"#/H5082\">H5082</a>, <a href=\"#/H5114\">H5114</a>"}]}